dc_description_s: Map shows populated areas, shantytowns, roads, cemeteries, and notable features. Includes city location map, boundaries index, and glossary. "Map information as of 1992." "This sheet falls within NB 38-14, 1501, 1:250,000 and NB 38-136, Y630, 1:100,000." "Printed by DMAHTC 12-92." "DMA stock no. Y921XXUDDER." "This map is red-light readable." "A lane is considered as being a minimum of 2.5 meters in width. Normal railroad gauge is 1.44 meters (4ʹ8.5ʹʹ)." "Caution: This product may not conform to the horizontal accuracy requirements. Extreme caution should be used when making measurements." ©Copyright 1992 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C.
